 width=\"1/3\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Treatments for common ailments</h4>\r\n<p>Such as colds, flu poison ivy, respiratory infections, bronchitis, pink eye, sinus problems, allergies, urinary tract infections, and ear infections[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=\"padding-4-percent\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color=\"#f1f0ed\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link_target=\"_self\" width=\"1/3\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Quick response</h4>\r\n<p>With a 10-minute average doctor response time[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"top\" column_margin=\"default\" bottom_padding=\"2%\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column_inner column_padding=\"padding-4-percent\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color=\"#f1f0ed\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link_target=\"_self\" width=\"1/3\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Visit records</h4>\r\n<p>Upon request, Teladoc can share visit information with your doctor[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=\"padding-4-percent\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color=\"#f1f0ed\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link_target=\"_self\" width=\"1/3\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>All ages</h4>\r\n<p>Visits are available for all ages — from children to seniors[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=\"padding-4-percent\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color=\"#f1f0ed\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link_target=\"_self\" width=\"1/3\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Experience</h4>\r\n<p>U.S. board-certified doctors with an average of 20 years practice experience[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/tab][tab icon_family=\"none\" title=\"DOCTORS ONLINE\" id=\"1550017550178-2\" tab_id=\"1550017550180-0\"][vc_row_inner column_margin=\"default\" top_padding=\"5%\" text_align=\"center\"][vc_column_inner column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link_target=\"_self\" width=\"1/1\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\" column_border_width=\"none\" column_border_style=\"solid\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Doctors Online\" font_container=\"tag:h3|font_size:40px|text_align:center|color:%23756e67\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1550016366884{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][divider line_type=\"Small Line\" line_alignment=\"center\" line_thickness=\"1\" divider_color=\"extra-color-2\" custom_line_width=\"50\"][divider line_type=\"No Line\" custom_height=\"30\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner column_margin=\"default\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column_inner column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link